PANDEMIA a.k.a. MEDICUS II

Simple demo of a location based MMO game for Android.

Virus infection and mutation, location based.

Using MQTT protocol and MapDB.

WORK IN PROGRESS!

Note: This game is not production ready, it's just a demo.

Note: The MQTT broker configured in GameService.java may be offline at any time, so get your own.
If you own a linux server somewhere on the internet, just install mosquitto (mosquitto.org) and you are done.
Also see mqtt.org for details about the "internet protocol of things".

